                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020217-84-off448 t18020217-84-cd449"></join>, a handkerchief, value 2s.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t18020217-84-victim844" type="victimName">
                  John 
